'''Keep Gaming''' is a Brazilian multi-gaming organization.

== History ==
The organization is mostly known for its Overwatch team and Hearthstone players, and joined the League of Legends scene after acquiring [[Big Gods]]' spot for [[Brazilian Challenger Circuit/2017 Season/Split 1|BRCC 2017]].

